---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Donut Cove Consulting | Custom Software Development Team" 
  description="Meet the custom software developers at Donut Cove Consulting. We specialize in process automation, internal tools, and system integrations for growing businesses in Minneapolis and beyond."
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Organic Blobs -->
  <section class="relative pt-20 md:pt-32 pb-32 md:pb-48 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Organic Background Blobs -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-coral/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10">
      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-6xl md:text-8xl tracking-tight leading-[0.95] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-8 drop-shadow-sm">
        About<br />
        <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Our Team</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
        We're software developers who build tools that actually work. We specialize in automating repetitive tasks, connecting your existing systems, and creating custom applications that fit how your business operates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-24 relative">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-6 max-w-4xl mr-auto">
          <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
            The Problem<br />
            <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">We Solve</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We've seen too many teams waste hours on data entry, manual reporting, and juggling disconnected systems. Your team should focus on solving real problems and making decisions, not copying data between spreadsheets.
            </p>
            <p>
              At Donut Cove Consulting, we build software that automates the repetitive stuff and connects your existing tools. Technology should make work easier, not add more complexity to your day.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 ml-auto max-w-4xl text-right md:text-right">
          <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
            Our<br />
            <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Approach</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We start by understanding your actual workflows—not what the manual says, but what people actually do every day. Then we identify where time gets wasted and build automated solutions that free your team to focus on the work that drives results.
            </p>
            <p>
              We work closely with your team throughout each project. You know your business best, so we listen first. Then we build solutions that fit into your existing operations without disrupting what's already working.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every solution we build has one goal: <strong class="text-coral-vibrant">make your team's work easier</strong>. We write code that works reliably, integrates with what you already have, and saves time from day one. No fluff, no over-engineering—just tools that solve real problems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center space-y-6 mb-20">
        <div class="text-tech-purple font-display font-semibold text-lg tracking-wide uppercase">Our Values</div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
          What Drives<br />
          <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Us Forward</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          These core principles guide every decision we make and every solution we build.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Innovation First</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We use proven technologies and practical approaches to solve real problems. We choose tools based on what works, not what's trendy.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Collaborative Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We work as part of your team, not as an outside vendor. We make sure every solution fits your business goals and your team's actual workflows.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Performance Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Every solution is built for speed, reliability, and measurable results. You'll see the impact quickly—less time on repetitive tasks, fewer errors, and more time for the work that matters.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Technical Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We use modern development practices and proven technologies to build maintainable, secure applications that developers love to work with.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Continuous Improvement</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We stay current with industry best practices and continuously refine our development processes to deliver even better results.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-coral-vibrant rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-300"></div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Client Success</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Your success is our success. We measure our impact by the tangible improvements in your business operations and team happiness.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-coral/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-8 relative z-10">
      <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
        Ready to<br />
        <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Get Started?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's talk about how we can help automate your repetitive tasks and free up your team's time. <a href="/services" class="text-coral-vibrant hover:underline">See our services</a> or <a href="/case-studies" class="text-coral-vibrant hover:underline">check out our results</a>.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-coral-vibrant text-white px-12 py-6 rounded-full font-bold text-xl hover:bg-coral hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-coral/20">
        Start the Conversation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 